                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">The handwriting appears very irregular throughout the Ms. Though very unusual, it appears that up to four different scribes were involved in copying. Abrupt changes in the size, shape and density is visible: <!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
