                     <handNote xml:id="h7" script="Ethiopic">
The words እግዚእ፡ (እግዚአብሔር፡)is sometimes written with, sometimes without the ligature (e.g., fol. 4va).<!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h8" script="Ethiopic">
Sometimes a change occurs in the middle of a word, coinciding with the end of a column, e.g., fols. 44rb-44va (ጴጥሮስ), 45ra-b(ማርያም).<!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
